name: Urbantopia (DistUrban Serie-1)
description:
Dystopia in the urban night... I see lights and explosions of thoughts formed in the shadow of the moonlight or in sordid alleys, I don't know if the thoughts are distorted by bad lighting or if this state was derived for the proliferation of bad illuminations... explosions of ideas in the pitch of utopia in the city's womb-tomb..

Edited night photo black and white.

Brasil-2021.
